column2: select enrollment.SystemStudentID   ,enrollment.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade   ,enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit   ,enrollment.isActiveEnrollment   ,emotion.score as Emotion_Score   from Enrollment enrollment   left join EmotionalScreener emotion   on enrollment.SystemStudentID = emotion.StudentID   and enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit = emotion.SchoolYear4Digit group by enrollment.SystemStudentID   ,enrollment.GradeLevel   ,enrollment.SchoolYear4Digit   ,enrollment.isActiveEnrollment
